metadata.title: In-akustik Soundcheck
description: Which cable is suitable for your requirements? This CD helps you to choose the right one. Because the cable has a huge impact on the sound of your hi-fi system. This CD contains a collection of superior recordings from the in-akustik sales repertoire representing all the different sound characteristics. You can enjoy exquisite music and the superior sound of your hi-fi system, once you have found the right cable. Includes tracks from Friedemann, Monty Alexander, Blues Company, Schenker Barden Acoustic Project, Sara K and more.
